  "detailed_description": "<strong>Crystalreach Islands</strong> is an open-world action RPG. Battle various enemies, gather gear, explore the world and fly the skies around the islands.<br>Experience the fantasy setting by getting to know the world, progress your character by gathering gear, items and unlocking skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/2c02324591a38da2bc3f5ddc2c4ea146.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/2c02324591a38da2bc3f5ddc2c4ea146.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/2c02324591a38da2bc3f5ddc2c4ea146.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Progress</strong><br>Mix the different equipment together without any class or level limits and make the perfect build for your style of gameplay. If you can get the gear, you can wear it. Experience a variety of stats that armor pieces give and experiment with various combinations. Try the differing abilities the weapons you obtain give you and unlock skills to compliment your weapon of choice.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/b94caaf0ed57adf69edf7c08905a3222.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/b94caaf0ed57adf69edf7c08905a3222.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/b94caaf0ed57adf69edf7c08905a3222.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battle</strong><br>Pick between three combat styles of using melee, magic or ranged weapons freely. Battle a variety of melee and projectile enemies with unique loot drops and find the weapon that best suits your play style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/0a0af9cbea9b449fc2490a66b9e10bd4.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/0a0af9cbea9b449fc2490a66b9e10bd4.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/0a0af9cbea9b449fc2490a66b9e10bd4.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore</strong><br>Visit the islands, discover and explore the dungeons, reach for the skies and the world hovering above you. Visit the towns around, visit the shops, have a chat with the inhabitant characters and discover opportunities awaiting you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/8fe45b08b24ee35a847bab6f08d3206d.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/8fe45b08b24ee35a847bab6f08d3206d.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/8fe45b08b24ee35a847bab6f08d3206d.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Crystalreach Islands</strong> is an open-world action RPG. Battle various enemies, gather gear, explore the world and fly the skies around the islands.<br>Experience the fantasy setting by getting to know the world, progress your character by gathering gear, items and unlocking skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/2c02324591a38da2bc3f5ddc2c4ea146.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/2c02324591a38da2bc3f5ddc2c4ea146.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/2c02324591a38da2bc3f5ddc2c4ea146.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Progress</strong><br>Mix the different equipment together without any class or level limits and make the perfect build for your style of gameplay. If you can get the gear, you can wear it. Experience a variety of stats that armor pieces give and experiment with various combinations. Try the differing abilities the weapons you obtain give you and unlock skills to compliment your weapon of choice.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/b94caaf0ed57adf69edf7c08905a3222.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/b94caaf0ed57adf69edf7c08905a3222.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/b94caaf0ed57adf69edf7c08905a3222.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battle</strong><br>Pick between three combat styles of using melee, magic or ranged weapons freely. Battle a variety of melee and projectile enemies with unique loot drops and find the weapon that best suits your play style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/0a0af9cbea9b449fc2490a66b9e10bd4.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/0a0af9cbea9b449fc2490a66b9e10bd4.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/0a0af9cbea9b449fc2490a66b9e10bd4.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore</strong><br>Visit the islands, discover and explore the dungeons, reach for the skies and the world hovering above you. Visit the towns around, visit the shops, have a chat with the inhabitant characters and discover opportunities awaiting you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/8fe45b08b24ee35a847bab6f08d3206d.poster.avif?t=1668035488\" width=700 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/8fe45b08b24ee35a847bab6f08d3206d.webm?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683870/extras/8fe45b08b24ee35a847bab6f08d3206d.mp4?t=1668035488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
